---
const benefits = [
  {
    title: "Tailor-Made Classes",
    description:
      "Forget generic methods. With me, every lesson is designed exclusively for you. Do you need to prepare for a trip? Do you need to practice your speaking skills? Or do you simply dream of understanding your favorite shows without subtitles? Together, we'll create the perfect plan for you to achieve your goals!",
  },
  {
    title: "Learn from a Native Speaker",
    description:
      "Not only is Spanish my first language, but I also thoroughly understand its complexities and, most importantly, I know how to teach them to you in an effective and fun way.",
  },
  {
    title: "Flexibility and Adaptability",
    description:
      "I understand that every student is unique. My classes adapt to your pace, your interests, and your learning style. Your progress is my priority!",
